creator: Futasaji LLC
descriptionHtml:
--------------------
How to use
--------------------
- Register your plants
Register the names of the plants and vegetables you want to grow.

- Record watering and fertilizer
Press a button to record the timing of watering and fertilizing.

- Notes
You can keep a notebook to record your plants.

--------------------
Recommended for the following people
--------------------
- People who like gardening and growing plants.
- I am addicted to vegetable gardening.
- I forget to water my plants.
- Forgetting to water your plants. - Suffering from lack of water or overwatering.
- I want to record the date and time I watered and fertilized my plants.

--------------------
▼ Features
--------------------
1. simple and easy
2. record watering and fertilizing
3. notification function to prevent you from forgetting to water

creator: Futasaji LLC
descriptionHtml:
--------------------
How to use
--------------------
- Register your plants
Register the names of the plants and vegetables you want to grow.

- Record watering and fertilizer
Press a button to record the timing of watering and fertilizing.

- Notes
You can keep a notebook to record your plants.

--------------------
Recommended for the following people
--------------------
- People who like gardening and growing plants.
- I am addicted to vegetable gardening.
- I forget to water my plants.
- Forgetting to water your plants. - Suffering from lack of water or overwatering.
- I want to record the date and time I watered and fertilized my plants.

--------------------
▼ Features
--------------------
1. simple and easy
2. record watering and fertilizing
3. notification function to prevent you from forgetting to water

Translated with www.DeepL.com/Translator (free version)
descriptionShort: Plant Care App. Watering reminders and plant diary.

descriptionHtml:
--------------------
How to use
--------------------
- Register your plants
Register the names of the plants and vegetables you want to grow.

- Record watering and fertilizer
Press a button to record the timing of watering and fertilizing.

- Notes
You can keep a notebook to record your plants.

--------------------
Recommended for the following people
--------------------
- People who like gardening and growing plants.
- I am addicted to vegetable gardening.
- I forget to water my plants.
- Forgetting to water your plants. - Suffering from lack of water or overwatering.
- I want to record the date and time I watered and fertilized my plants.

--------------------
▼ Features
--------------------
1. simple and easy
2. record watering and fertilizing
3. notification function to prevent you from forgetting to water

Translated with www.DeepL.com/Translator (free version)
descriptionShort: Plant Care App. Watering reminders and plant diary.
